  "title": "Dungeoneer",
  "summary": "<p><em>Dungeoneer</em> is a series of 64 works in a self-running program that navigates a generative maze, raycasting images onto bricked walls as an NPC moves through a programmatic path. Each image serves as a portal to a dungeon floor … a figure tied to memory, used as texture for an endlessly repetitive pixel terrain.</p>\n<p>( CLICK/TAP IMAGE TO ENTER )</p>\n",
